      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/27/1/33/4",
      "text": [
        ": أوصى أبو الحسن عليه السلام إلى ابنه الحسن عليه السلام قبل مضيه بأربعة أشهر،وأشهدني على ذلك وجماعة من الموالي."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayyid-athar-husain-s-h-rizvi": [
          "H 166 - Yahya bin Bashr Qambari has narrated that Abul Hasan Imam Hadi (a.s), four months before he passed away, made bequest to his son, Hasan (a.s) and I and a group of Shia witnessed it."
        ]
      }
